{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_amgoat_set_2_story_1","storyGroup":"story_amgoat_set_2","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"火山","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"火山夺走了艾雅法拉的父母，也给予了她满身伤痛，可她依然平静地走在探寻真理的道路上。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_amgoat_2_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["艾雅法拉","干员巴蒂"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"text","text":"4:32 P. M. 天气/阴","id":7},{"type":"text","text":"莱塔尼亚北部荒原 火山带7号采样点","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"......请您放心，本次任务顺利进入尾声，艾雅法拉小姐很疲惫，不过健康状况基本稳定。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"本次调查的具体结果尚且不明，从艾雅法拉小姐的反应来看，应该有些小小的、难称突破的进展。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"回程路上，我会继续确保她......","id":11},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":12,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_bg_bg_desert_3.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"巴蒂先生？","id":19,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":21},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"啊......啊！艾雅法拉小姐，有、有什么事吗？","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"那个......左前方最近那个采样点的设备似乎偏移了一点，实时数据的背景噪声突然有些波动......","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"您能不能帮忙看下是怎么回事？","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"对、对不起！","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"咦？","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"是我刚才动了一下！实在很抱歉，我我我不是有意要看数据——","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"唔......原来巴蒂先生是在看数据？","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"咳、咳咳咳......","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"这样啊......那没事啦。我本来还以为是风太大导致的，这么看的话也不用检查其他采样设备了。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"呼......咦？居然一点都没生气？","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"艾雅法拉小姐不怪我随便看数据吗？","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"......怪？我、我不是很确定有没有听清楚......巴蒂先生是说我有没有觉得奇怪吗？","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"要说奇怪的话，是有一点。没想到巴蒂先生也会对这些研究数据有兴趣呢。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哈哈......确实。像我这样的大老粗......","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"没那回事啦。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"只是火山方面的研究不算热门，大多数时候就是像这样跑到荒地里，坐着观察一整天，然后埋头分析数据......一般人都会觉得枯燥吧？","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"要说枯燥的话，这世上绝大多数人的生活都很枯燥啊。","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"每天起床，吃东西，白天忙着各种活计，到了晚上就一觉睡过去。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"比起来，像艾雅法拉小姐这样学者，可是在永远都在和新鲜事物打交道。这起码有意义多了！","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"......","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"......笑、笑了！是我说的话太傻了吗？","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"没有没有。巴蒂先生刚刚说话的语气，听起来有一点点像我过去认识的学校里的人哦。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哈哈，这个嘛，毕竟我过去也是和大学里的人打过交道的。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"诶？巴蒂先生不是一直从事安保方面的工作吗？","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哎呀，好久以前的事了。那会我在......承蒙一位年轻教员的关照，才有了起步的工作机会。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"他帮助了我许多，也让我认识到做研究是一件有意义而且......呃，怎么说呢，没那么简单的事。对，没那么简单。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"5","id":70},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"character","id":72},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":74},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":77},{"type":"text","text":"......通过上次与凯尔希医生的交谈，知悉巴蒂先生目前在罗德岛就职，还有件事想要拜托......","id":78},{"type":"text","text":"是关于瑙曼小姐......她目前在罗德岛的代号叫做艾雅法拉。","id":79},{"type":"text","text":"她是我恩师唯一的孩子......","id":80},{"type":"text","text":"希望巴蒂先生能尽量关照这个孩子。","id":81},{"type":"text","text":"不仅仅是身体方面，她的矿石病确实已相当凶险......","id":82},{"type":"text","text":"还有她的研究工作。","id":83},{"type":"text","text":"请务必关注她的进展情况，有必要时麻烦与我联系。","id":84},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":85,"musicid":1},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"卡恩先生......","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"出行之前凯尔希医生把这封信转交给我，但她应该很清楚，哪怕没有您的委托，我也会保护好艾雅法拉小姐。","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":88},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"character","id":90},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_bg_bg_desert_3.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"说起来，艾雅法拉小姐第一次火山考察是在好几年前了吧？","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"嗯，第一次考察的话......好像有三年多啦。","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哎呀，那时候艾雅法拉小姐还是个小孩子啊！","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"（小声）现在的研究机构都这么黑心的吗？","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"目前助听器工作很正常，我都听到了哦巴蒂先生。","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":103},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"啊，我不是在说罗德岛，千、千万别误会！","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"开个玩笑......其实威廉大学也没有啦，当时学校并不支持我这么早就参与进来。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"只是，爸爸妈妈留下的资料，有些内容只有我能解读。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我不希望项目中断......我觉得爸爸妈妈也不希望项目中断。是我坚持要代替他们加入下一次实地考察的。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"爸爸妈妈......啊！抱歉抱歉，差点忘了艾雅法拉小姐的父母已经......","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"没关系的巴蒂先生，已经过去很久了。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"就是因为......火山？","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"嗯......火山很危险。妈妈从小就这么跟我说。","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"——光火焰就能轻松吞噬掉一栋房子。火山的话，是肚子里装满了能量的庞然巨物。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"巨物或许没有多余的想法，可是当它张开嘴，随意地呼吸或者咳嗽——它就会改变大地。","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"说来有些好笑，我很小的时候，并不能真正理解爸爸妈妈的工作。那时候在我心里，爸爸妈妈是挑战巨物的勇士。","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哎，说是勇士也不为过吧？明知危险，却还是坚持去做。这需要多大的勇气啊！","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"......也会害怕的。","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我第一次亲眼看到火山的时候......我的眼睛还不像现在这样。我能看得很清楚。我的耳朵也还灵敏。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我到现在都记得那片奔涌着的赤红色，还有耳畔巨大的声响......就好像有怪物要挣脱大地的束缚，咆哮着爬到跟前来。","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"和所有书上写的、画的都不一样......它是活着的巨物。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我......我的腿就像僵住了似的。我走不动路。我甚至好一阵都没敢呼气，直到再也憋不住，咳嗽咳得眼泪都流了下来。","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"那一瞬间，我就明白了。","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"明白......了？","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"嗯，我明白了很多事。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"明白了为什么每一次外出考察之前，妈妈都要挤到我的小床上，紧紧抱着我直到我睡过去。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"明白了为什么每一次考察归来，爸爸一边整理着资料，一边总会过来摸摸我的脑袋，嘴里不断说着“真是太好啦”。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"大概......他们每一次都是怀着这种害怕的心情出发的吧。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"唉。遇到这样的事，艾雅法拉小姐居然还能坚持下去，真的很了不起。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"我听说过很多类似的悲剧，比如心爱的孩子被河流吞噬，从此父母就怨恨上了河流，飞快搬了家。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"类似的话......好像当时也有人说过。","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"爸爸妈妈出事的第二天，有很多叔叔阿姨哥哥姐姐找过我，尤其是听说我想加入火山考察的队伍之后。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我很理解也很感谢他们。他们就是担心我会心生怨恨，做一些冲动的傻事吧。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"他们中的大部分都希望我能放下一切，继续正常地上学。可是我做不到。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"所以艾雅法拉小姐......心里一点都不恨吗？","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":147},{"type":"character","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":150},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":153},{"type":"text","text":"......在瑙曼教授出事之后，我一直在苦苦追寻事故的原因......","id":154},{"type":"text","text":"我不相信一位最顶尖的火山学家，与她精通源石技艺的丈夫，会死于一场平平无奇的火山灾害。","id":155},{"type":"text","text":"他们的研究早就吸引了过多的目光。在道路前方等着的并不仅仅是真相。","id":156},{"type":"text","text":"有人希望能更透彻地利用这些成果，还有人希望这些结果永远地在火山碎屑流下埋葬。","id":157},{"type":"text","text":"......阿黛尔还小，我不确定她是否能理解这研究背后的危险。在乌云聚拢之前，她又不幸感染了矿石病。","id":158},{"type":"text","text":"我信任罗德岛，就如凯尔希医生也信任我一般。","id":159},{"type":"text","text":"只是如果可能的话，我希望阿黛尔能停下来......凯尔希医生却说，我应当看看她如今成长后的模样。","id":160},{"type":"text","text":"手头的工作令我无法脱身，因此我让凯尔希医生找到了你，巴蒂先生。","id":161},{"type":"text","text":"请替我好好看看这孩子......","id":162},{"type":"text","text":"我希望在一切进行到无可挽回之前，尽可能地在那些乌云背后的注视之下，保护她、令她的身心不至于受到外界深重的伤害。","id":163},{"type":"dialog","id":164},{"type":"character","id":165},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_bg_bg_desert_3.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":167},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"不管怎么说，火山夺去了你的父母，还导致了......你的病......","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"唔......","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"一定要说怨恨的话......也还是有一点的。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"不，不对。与其说是怨恨，应该说是难过吧。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我很想爸爸......也很想妈妈。刚刚听说他们出事的消息，我不敢相信那是真的。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"爸爸的源石技艺明明那么厉害......妈妈过去都完成了那么多次实地考察。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"那几个晚上我都是稀里糊涂睡着，梦里总会看到想象中的火山，然后大喊大叫或者哭着醒过来......完全没有巴蒂先生说得那么了不起。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"不不不！这都是人之常情啊！而且艾雅法拉小姐当时还那么小！","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"这么想的话，一边做着考察工作，一边还要照顾一个哭哭啼啼的小女孩，当时考察队的哥哥姐姐真的都很不容易。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"唔......果然有机会还是要多写几封感谢信啊。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哈哈哈......","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"好在这种崩溃的情绪，在我第一次亲眼看到火山之后，就慢慢好了起来。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"咦？我记得艾雅法拉小姐刚才说感到害怕......","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"嗯，是很害怕。除了害怕之外，也感觉到了一丝平静。巴蒂先生一定觉得很难理解吧？","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"平静吗？确实......我没有想到。","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我当时不可避免地想到了爸爸妈妈。那一瞬间我突然想到，他们看到的火山，是不是和我看到的火山一样呢？","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"过去的学者，看到的火山也是这样吧？哪怕再过去几百年——无论是不是同一个地点，这些红色的岩浆可能仍像此刻一样活跃着啊。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"而就算我没有得病，也不出什么意外，用我一辈子的时间去尝试着研究它、理解它，我对面前的永恒巨物，又能够了解多少？","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"“为什么爸爸妈妈会选这条路？”，“为什么爸爸妈妈会死？”","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"这些问题的答案......相比眼前这个永恒的问题来说，突然就没那么重要了。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"留给我的时间太少太少啦。我好像，真的没有借口退缩，也没有借口继续悲伤和恐惧下去。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"艾雅法拉小姐......","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我想，爸爸妈妈也是这个想法。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我拿着他们留给我的资料，走着他们走过的路。就好像，他们从来没有离开这个世界一样。他们活在我的正前方，引领着我继续往前。","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"如果......有一天我也不得不离开这个世界，也还是会有人继承我留下的成果，不断不断地往前走吧？","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"真是厉害，这么一来，一个传一个的，不断掉的话，就好像另一种永恒一样。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"唔......永恒吗？我没想过......咳咳咳......","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哎呀，风是不是又变大了？","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"请往这边坐一点吧艾雅法拉小姐，你的身体禁不住风吹。","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"咳咳......谢谢。嗯，现在这样好多啦。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"今天说了这么一大堆，可能巴蒂先生会有误会......说实话，我没那么勇敢。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我总是......总是忍不住回想几年前外出考察的时候。","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"那时候我比现在好得多，虽然也没那么强壮，可至少不会磕磕碰碰，给人添麻烦。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"没有没有，一点都不麻烦，艾雅法拉小姐可厉害着呢。这一路上是你照顾我们更多。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"冷......风、风好大......","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":222},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"呜......已经把衣服都穿上了......手和脚还是会止不住地哆嗦。","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"诶，刚才就想说，艾雅法拉小姐似乎很怕冷的样子，但我们在靠近你的时候会觉得很烫啊。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"那是我的源石技艺......可能因为主观感受上太冷了吧，所以会不由自主地用上一些法术。","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"抱歉巴蒂先生，如果不希望被烫伤的话，请稍微离我远一些。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哎呀，没关系，如果能好受一些的话，温度再高一些也没事，不用在意我。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"......没什么用的啦。只是无意识的反应，最多也就是带来一丝心理安慰，结果还是在这里丢人地瑟瑟发抖。","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"拥有这种源石技艺，又是卡普里尼，巴蒂先生是不是觉得我不该这么怕冷？","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"其实......其实，我以前一点都不怕冷的。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"唉......","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"没事的，下、下次，再多带一些衣服吧！","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"嗯，再多带一些衣服......","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"还有好好调整下助听器。总是听了一半闹笑话，巴蒂先生也很头疼吧？","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"那个......艾雅法拉小姐......你的，呃，你的腿......","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"诶？我的腿怎么啦？","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"啊......好像自己动起来了......","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"哈哈，是在打节拍吧？因为那家伙啊，那家伙远远地在那边坐着，自顾自哼了好久歌了。","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":249},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"嗯？","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":252},{"type":"character","id":253},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_068","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":255},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_storyendjp_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":256,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":257},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":258},{"type":"text","text":"♪雪一直在下","id":259},{"type":"text","text":"♪万物静了，渐渐地静了","id":260},{"type":"text","text":"♪我爱这支舞，更爱远方的群山","id":261},{"type":"text","text":"♪我的希望与渴望","id":262},{"type":"text","text":"♪在这自由的大地上","id":263},{"type":"text","text":"♪将无人可以阻挡","id":264},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":266},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"我好像听到了......又好像没有......","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾雅法拉","text":"唔......这是小时候听过的歌啊。不知不觉，脑子里一直在回响。","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_180_amgoat.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_180_amgoat","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"也、也跟着哼起来了......","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"干员巴蒂","text":"看着这样的艾雅法拉小姐，突然就觉得很平静。","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":273},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":274},{"type":"character","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":277},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"text","text":"卡恩先生，关于您委托之事——","id":279},{"type":"dialog","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":281},{"type":"text","text":"您认为她或许正处在危险之中，深陷纷争的漩涡，担心她的心灵会受到伤害，因此委托我对瑙曼小姐——艾雅法拉小姐多加关注。","id":282},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":284},{"type":"text","text":"我理解您的担忧，可同时也必须对您指出——","id":285},{"type":"dialog","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":287},{"type":"text","text":"这种担忧，对艾雅法拉小姐来说，也许是不必要的。","id":288},{"type":"dialog","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":290},{"type":"text","text":"她的心经火山岩浆熔炼，是这世上最坚硬纯粹之物。","id":291},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":293},{"type":"text","text":"我想，那些跟随而来的乌云根本撼动不了她。","id":294},{"type":"dialog","id":295},{"type":"character","id":296},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":297},{"type":"image","id":298}],"characters":["艾雅法拉","干员巴蒂"]}